We ask that you have your way now during this time of invitation and response.

00:36:12.115 --> 00:36:14.740
We pray that each one of us would respond as you're calling us to do.

00:36:15.321 --> 00:36:17.304
In Jesus' name we pray, amen.

00:36:17.384 --> 00:36:18.546
Please stand and you come.
